(30030,'Gratis, RSNU Jombang Fasilitasi Pengurusan Akta Kelahiran dan KK bagi Pasien Melahirkan',2,125,'Kini, para ibu yang melahirkan di RSNU Jombang mendapatkan kemudahan berupa fasilitasi pengurusan Kartu Keluarga (KK) serta Akta Kelahiran anak secara gratis. Khutbah Jumat Tahun Baru 2026: Mengevaluasi Diri, Raih Ridha Ilahi Berikut Lafal Doa Awal dan Akhir Tahun di tengah Maraknya Bencana Khutbah Jumat Tahun Baru: Mari Manfaatkan Waktu dengan Baik Jadwal Puasa Sunnah Sepanjang Januari 2026 Khutbah Jumat: Muhasabah di Awal Tahun, Menata Hidup dengan Ketakwaan Khutbah Jumat: Rajab, Bulan Istighfar dan Peningkatan Ketakwaan Bantuan Tak Merata dan Jalan Rusak, Warga Bener Meriah: Kami yang di Pelosok Tidak Tersentuh PCINU Taiwan dan KDEI Pulangkan 130 Jenazah WNI ke Tanah Air Awal 2026, Korban Meninggal Dunia Bencana Aceh-Sumatra Capai 1.157 Jiwa Menembus Medan Terjal dari Bener Meriah, Pasukan Bagana Salurkan Bantuan ke Aceh Tengah Prabowo soal Bantuan Asing untuk Bencana Sumatra: Bodoh Kalau Kita Tolak','[0.032107413,0.02376456,-0.06826841,-0.008296371,-0.089740805,0.016539136,0.033781677,-0.014020705,-0.010682959,-0.0055754296,0.10751558,-0.024666458,0.03596486,-0.056904465,0.054105535,-0.027566256,0.0016908303,0.032929864,-0.11909245,-0.044439245,-0.036492422,-0.05150351,-0.032903705,-0.04726995,-0.08322019,0.045004796,0.00063031213,-0.0506317,0.05432067,0.0037855774,0.036155242,0.09591559,0.059285387,-0.042195268,0.0044538425,0.044619963,-0.011287374,0.02478111,0.061219353,0.01704451,-0.021520277,-0.07995704,-0.043044057,-0.1409644,0.10589734,-0.04109,-0.08839026,-0.035912495,0.017048625,-0.0027774177,-0.07415231,-0.01660618,0.056627855,0.0058949585,0.044108633,-0.13482946,-0.023976,0.03766329,-0.002784414,-0.045235522,0.049616233,0.06361536,-0.011113189,-0.03309756,0.089954175,-0.07892797,-0.053902972,-0.008907772,0.023237176,-0.007181425,-0.007921421,-0.04414009,-0.059302904,0.065232016,-0.089473784,-0.0059912507,0.04954069,0.058571327,0.056144617,-0.04467025