(30069,'Borderline Personality Disorder Test',2,160,'Individuals with borderline personality disorder struggle with relationships and emotional regulation. They may cling to those close to them and react with fury at the slightest sign that they are pulling away. Those with BPD may neither recognize or acknowledge it, but when they get help, the majority can stabilize their lives. Is someone you know living with BPD? This test can help you find out. Using the key below, answer the questions based on how strongly you agree or disagree with the statement. This test is for anyone curious about borderline personality disorder, or concerned that they (or someone close to them) may be experiencing the condition. If you are concerned that someone close to you has borderline personality disorder or that you might be living with it yourself, you can speak to a mental health professional about ways to address it. You can find a clinician in the Psychology Today Therapy Directory.','[-0.014084229,0.111091636,-0.041227043,0.07203608,-0.055028245,0.018407416,0.1004492,0.11819936,-0.07330499,0.0789488,0.08546404,-0.07625192,-0.08449866,0.030342588,0.023990747,0.0139870355,0.015102517,0.019007407,-0.07168476,0.05403104,-0.044248283,0.074404664,-0.02238939,-0.0372273,-0.09214896,0.027579127,0.012540858,-0.057895627,0.057045966,-0.03310337,0.028611775,0.10195678,0.07749995,0.052543048,0.022598866,-0.012308375,0.036072824,0.052535597,0.05296766,-0.01161327,0.025824625,0.082804136,0.0050151437,-0.023879647,-0.027366938,-0.06603382,-0.11369251,0.019638667,-0.019554598,-0.04196996,-0.113099284,-0.022280421,0.014763839,0.0075633265,0.030416287,-0.046343535,0.063029885,0.12388765,-0.021212159,-0.006964663,0.0013615292,0.0031768994,-0.0028792159,-0.049411565,0.11675014,-0.047948446,-0.0046544136,-0.0011627673,0.06437804,0.01201421,0.090370126,-0.037598275,-0.005213026,0.009033573,0.003952078,0.04329698,-0.014393057,0.029931279,0.060386818,-0.0011144859,-0.053886537,0.003709323,0.010974109,