(30133,'5 Alasan Hubungan Cinta Lintas Generasi yang Perlu Dipahami Tanpa Prasangka, dari Riset Psikologi hingga Nilai Budaya.',2,218,'Namun, hubungan lintas usia juga menghadirkan tantangan emosional tersendiri. Studi longitudinal di Korea Selatan (2006–2012) menemukan bahwa pasangan dengan jarak usia ≥ 3 tahun mengalami tingkat kepuasan yang menurun seiring waktu—terutama jika keterampilan adaptasi emosionalnya rendah. Hal ini diduga berkaitan dengan perbedaan tahap perkembangan psikologis dan ekspektasi, yang bisa makin kompleks jika tidak didasari keterikatan yang sehat. <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1138\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://cdn-prd.tongkolspac...','[0.013397962,0.051805574,0.048043165,-0.013287191,-0.061984215,0.022460658,-0.047971964,0.07759895,-0.014631429,-0.040811464,0.1661756,-0.033854183,0.047527876,-0.054036878,0.03282733,0.025346126,-0.017663086,0.08297537,-0.052092906,-0.058588494,-0.0043170745,-0.056229424,-0.029402332,-0.011674603,-0.015038212,0.0059048715,0.033789486,0.0060548736,0.08774786,-0.053995784,0.00846119,0.1077674,0.017768946,-0.006930044,0.0053703883,0.0589821,-0.05091167,-0.019162007,-0.05739049,0.03014593,-0.037157193,-0.10240683,-0.035833072,-0.13228568,0.0411178,-0.03453004,-0.05019586,-0.057016097,-0.09412689,-0.0059881182,-0.047040537,-0.029409816,-0.006140632,-0.006947139,-0.0224456,-0.10574148,-0.04878251,0.019231902,0.0068563954,0.0034364525,-0.00616034,0.010459571,-0.05816291,-0.04752242,0.08650403,0.04347493,-0.033428963,-0.018078215,0.045427866,0.012369609,0.033803172,-0.009661729,-0.015619549,0.055796105,-0.13850746,-0.014305233,0.05536316,0.049429636,0.05056525,-0.07694835,0.026348334,0.08359236,-0.027476331,-0.0031691839,-0.058980815,-0.0069398503,-0.120856546,0.022498297,-0.11944562,0.02129732,0.081982955,0.07831037,-0.07891533,-0.023617635,-0.015479146,0.041247018,-0.13361,-0.03584535,0.04779719,-0.011988335,0.01096063,0.03387362,0.00861997,0.046724457,-0.082454845,-0.06093264,-0.018615676,-0.12046741,0.02159