(30141,'Do You Know Proven Psychology Facts?',2,225,'Over the last two decades, psychology has confronted a replication crisis in the field—much research doesn’t hold up to scrutiny. Psychologists have been working to solve these problems and strengthen the field’s reliability. At the same time, there are some core discoveries, psychological truths, that have strong support. Take this quiz to assess your knowledge of important psychological findings. We can help you find a match. It’s free and we verify all therapist credentials. We can help you find a match. It’s free and we verify all therapist credentials.','[-0.054434564,0.04445398,-0.048838302,-0.07761776,-0.13414386,-0.023112243,0.10700963,0.014136983,0.02401994,0.02988495,0.12297217,0.043685302,-0.0444467,0.0032903848,-0.0010825299,0.024498072,-0.037676994,0.008913133,-0.12562384,-0.052385848,0.018690763,-0.04415846,-0.059722193,0.03565466,-0.03408684,0.009872787,-0.024395578,-0.021064823,0.11746058,-0.0012873547,0.015297529,0.0638962,0.017937828,-0.008729254,0.029445922,0.08824893,-0.018345581,-0.0063793957,0.015400905,0.031471834,-0.030943131,-0.07559547,-0.081900276,-0.108974844,0.03902051,-0.042212453,-0.10660641,0.02507328,0.033678822,-0.07147393,-0.12896182,0.018291563,0.04937833,0.0007398279,0.0006295403,-0.054478567,0.009520846,0.077922694,0.025308542,-0.05985043,0.006492671,0.05458666,-0.027060134,-0.0038390444,0.064656556,0.022502443,-0.14619368,0.018498268,0.07481599,0.031170188,-0.039625365,-0.01290488,-0.042090595,0.05133723,-0.07994478,-0.029434023,-0.023257023,-0.02453779,0.0065243985,-0.006600598,0.07120661,0.022428723,-0.00047793775,-0.022910388,-0.07315955,-0.0081184115,-0.030496463,0.04687015,-0.02083023,-0.0016314554,-0.025226492,0.016676519,0.0016044677,-0.072616346,-0.038782556,-0.036186166,-0.082693316,-0.043969285,0.009109309,0.03423521,0.004502215,-0.0057355496,-0.05557996,-0.02704912,-0.08495291,-0.06397735,0.030674784,-0.1007426,0.092230305,0.07383904,-0.097243704,-0.05433144,-0.055