(30156,'Psychiatry Through the Looking Glass',2,239,'A psychologist peers into psychiatry\'s past, present and future Personal Perspective: Searching for hope in 2026. Personal Perspective: Searching for hope in 2026. An international survey of 1144 electroconvulsive therapy (ECT) patients and relatives has found that the causes of the patients\' problems are ignored. An international survey of 1144 electroconvulsive therapy (ECT) patients and relatives has found that the causes of the patients\' problems are ignored. It is well established that the most common adverse effect of electroconvulsive therapy is memory loss. Our latest paper reports on 25 other adverse effects in multiple domains. It is well established that the most common adverse effect of electroconvulsive therapy is memory loss. Our latest paper reports on 25 other adverse effects in multiple domains. Women are twice as likely as men to be given electroconvulsive therapy. Our international survey shows they are less likely to benefit and more likely to suffer memory loss. Women are twice as likely as men to be given electroconvulsive therapy. Our international survey shows they are less likely to benefit and more likely to suffer memory loss. In our international survey, 71 percent of ECT patients reported reduced ability to retain new information, and 80 percent reported loss of autobiographical memories of events before ECT. In our international survey, 71 percent of ECT patients reported reduced ability to retain new information, and 80 percent reported loss of autobiographical memories of events before ECT. The first papers from an electroconvulsive therapy survey have been published. It found ECT to be either ineffective or damaging. The first papers from an electroconvulsive therapy survey have been published. It found ECT to be either ineffective or damaging. Although the most common side effect of Electroconvulsive Therapy is memory loss, my recent review suggests that more attention should be paid to major adverse cardiac events. Although the most common side effect of Electroconvulsive Therapy is memory loss, my recent review suggests that more attention should be paid to major adverse cardiac events. Research on ECT typically relies on the assessments of the psychiatrists who prescribed it. This international survey asks the patients themselves and their relatives instead. Research on ECT typically relies on the assessments of the psychiatrists who prescribed it. This international survey asks the patients themselves and their relatives instead. Considering cognitive dissonance and intergenerational trauma may help avoid one-sided responses to the tragedy in the Middle East. Considering cognitive dissonance and intergenerational trauma may help avoid one-sided responses to the tragedy in the Middle East. Opinion: The case for ECT to be made illegal for children and adolescents. Opinion: The case for ECT to be made illegal for children and adolescents. The UN and WHO have launched a blueprint for laws that prioritize the human rights of patients. The UN and WHO have launched a blueprint for laws that prioritize the human rights of patients. A survey of over 500 British antidepressant users found that most experienced severe withdrawal effects when they tried to stop, yet few received any help to come off safely. A survey of over 500 British antidepressant users found that most experienced severe withdrawal effects when they tried to stop, yet few received any help to come off safely. Electroconvulsive therapy has limited short-term benefits compared to placebo, and no long-term benefits. Are ECT patients being told the facts? Electroconvulsive therapy has limited short-term benefits compared to placebo, and no long-term benefits. Are ECT patients being told the facts? Hundreds of antidepressant users express dissatisfaction with their prescribing doctors regarding their recommendations for withdrawal from the drugs. Hundreds of antidepressant users express dissatisfaction with...','[0.048533443,0.067361645,-0.05456619,-0.009052802,-0.16114223,0.026990918,0.045022056,0.021723568,0.009006748,-0.01443762,0.116939954,-0.06385344,-0.023765953,-0.021695387,-0.009701614,-0.07104521,0.010704783,0.01851635,-0.055770647,-0.062653,0.009932811,0.014171687,0.037143063,-0.03902008,-0.018211808,0.014050112,-0.022579595,-0.045972586,0.060672205,-0.06976957,0.030306794,0.11367364,0.10583756,-0.056044172,-0.058083504,-0.02118936,-0.05538206,0.058396257,0.072834276,0.016837953,0.012552018,-0.048748802,-0.0760705,-0.104474515,0.059258793,-0.01627195,-0.048068542,-0.0007727429,-0.017475244,0.021099523,-0.111431815,0.0006802863,0.015936343,0.013808847,-0.0123465555,-0.15806864,0.056882527,-0.04010104,-0.0400419,-0.0127794985,0.023421315,0.052755315,-0.021792183,-0.048020866,0.005402998,-0.060709927,-0.023219882,-0.0067522144,0.038457114,0.012608644,0.016942076,0.0060580145,-0.02913979,0.084173046,-0.11588249,0.0061420742,-0.048488326,0.0086788,0.020163832,-0.05908515,0.06548262,0.04004943,-0.0065447134,0.046995483,-0.06588221,-0.032115273,-0.037194956,0.025032312,-0.074927956,0.018889667,0.041121498,0.039103318,-0.06372004,-0.07061572,-0.0049115075,0.009218467,-0.08348417,-0.024827762,-0.030227879,-0.002753766,0.0027500659,0.023626056,-0.033907205,0.025417378,-0.103177555,-0.07695033,-0.0005015535,-0.05775612,0.06977659,-0.0010141922,-0.09664924,-0.018064942,-0.122832306,-0.061952695,-0.00552488,-0.024874855,0.02133828,0.007194231,0.04268037,0.062246744,-0.026514556,-0.01933439,0.008433099,-0.043368943,0.034872707,-0.04438072,0.009984865,0.000000000000000000000000000000031028293,-0.006952155,-0.06977686,0.022170909,0.014073266,0.0032398496,-0.010338384,-0.0454405,-0.080421075,0.07281873,-0.1944517,-0.0068227933,-0.04424798,-0.00047613785,0.05129018,0.02562959,-0.003833674,-0.08361533,-0.0045952066,-0.017155483,-0.02160165,-0.00818587,-0.027370514,0.0059562423,-0.03402911,0.07286086,-0.036389377,-0.022843957,0.007450746,0.0032596823,0