(30214,'Bipolar Disorder',2,291,'The extreme highs and lows of bipolar disorder can damage your relationships and disrupt your daily life. But you’re not powerless. With treatment, support, and good coping skills, you can manage your disorder and keep symptoms in check. Treatment and therapy for managing bipolar disorder The role of medication in treatment and your different options How to support a friend or family member with bipolar disorder Self-help tips for managing bipolar symptoms Take this short quiz if you think you are bipolar Coping with addiction and a mental health problem Tips for overcoming depression one step at a time How it works and how to decide if it’s the right treatment for you','[-0.0247185,0.023348907,-0.065194614,0.03855486,-0.08087904,0.07503738,0.11217025,0.06385693,-0.00170057,0.007681541,0.04211588,-0.0030646578,-0.015740728,-0.007902993,0.08778251,0.060629405,0.013862998,-0.025705317,-0.031417128,0.03248973,0.012972353,-0.038542904,-0.05813785,0.015691997,-0.05001385,0.08022242,0.010761005,-0.042566705,0.08557326,0.056459986,0.014114282,0.13913542,0.054676414,0.051888525,-0.024588343,0.019271497,-0.04497688,0.045256793,0.0018450255,0.037827346,-0.013879586,0.07696627,-0.0028051916,-0.116187245,-0.0044686943,-0.100749254,-0.00920519,-0.026865184,-0.027058847,-0.10475047,-0.07068843,0.004487489,0.074995354,-0.027928306,0.043302342,-0.020390142,0.09023937,0.03150814,-0.021983653,0.060484964,-0.00871236,0.028820286,0.06661113,-0.094140634,0.086648494,0.04209729,-0.054996073,0.03724056,0.032572832,-0.030375712,0.0162831,-0.026631137,0.0019153078,0.055545714,0.029864782,-0.003464157,-0.01974422,0.032029614,0.019133233,-0.001654077,-0.056066487,0.059210606,0.006672244,-0.06424644,0.0324015,-0.039048497,0.02483543,0.059978135,-0.06098131,0.08132555,-0.011254799,-0.010176012,-0.015649064,-0.09810808,0.013146989,-0.036414184,-0.033886123,-0.037443954,-0.0060824202,-0.01918556,0.05153047,0.061716117,-0.04721417,0.033287127,-0.086721204,-0.083337