(30216,'Depression',2,293,'Depression is more than just feeling sad. It drains your optimism, energy, and drive. It can seem like there’s no way out. But no matter how bad you feel, there’s always hope. Read on to learn about symptoms, treatment, and recovery. What you need to know about depression medication Tips for overcoming depression one step at a time Signs, symptoms, and causes of female depression and what to do How to recognize depression in yourself and others Therapy, medication, and lifestyle changes that can help you feel better Supporting a depressed loved one while still taking care of yourself Recognizing the signs and symptoms, and helping your child','[0.05066322,0.1280505,-0.06812446,0.058139797,-0.011551418,-0.010717162,-0.015608889,0.07612503,0.021805674,0.049657013,0.0142524075,-0.066671714,-0.022467446,-0.0027045372,0.0018333873,0.047471467,-0.030984608,-0.042768706,-0.02666875,-0.0066226735,0.03208256,-0.018124085,-0.069839194,0.055850737,0.0067775007,0.012824687,-0.036384307,0.009850626,0.01075786,0.04060164,0.035136405,0.04331543,0.130393,-0.039249934,-0.022891106,0.053368956,-0.053491652,0.029534373,0.016332315,0.059109103,-0.035040732,-0.0021921399,-0.04607781,-0.092910044,0.03866093,-0.08832089,-0.013690162,0.0011065706,0.00069912814,-0.07895874,-0.073375344,0.011571054,-0.059828706,-0.050077952,0.018610656,-0.095675655,0.03293318,0.003856935,-0.044173967,-0.0021948193,0.018027965,0.028242424,0.0073000225,-0.02069669,0.08271807,-0.03397132,-0.019983586,0.030220067,0.009328758,0.011722672,0.025032328,-0.08028797,0.0060302964,0.05692389,-0.06489937,-0.0128261605,0.044579655,0.026327655,0.045047916,-0.014101511,0.06801679,0.05954205,0.010464715,-0.039100457,-0.028739827,-0.026122676,-0.0031352513,0.012781328,-0.027694685,0.0632376,0.019736564,-0.057647888,-0.02970774,-0.038042694,-0.036939632,-0.0033324875,-0.05897483,-0.04881301,-0.0061450815,-0.021057531,-0.0022349288,-0.061201658,-0.016384304,-0.055410247,-0.13267554,-0.05851582,0.00442