(30217,'Eating Disorders',2,294,'If you have an eating disorder, you may believe that if you can control what you eat, you’ll be able to control your life. But true confidence comes from accepting yourself for who you truly are—and that’s only possible with recovery. Signs, symptoms, causes, and treatment options for anorexia Symptoms, treatment and help for compulsive overeating Signs, symptoms, treatment and self-help tips How to overcome your eating disorder and gain true self-confidence Advice for parents, family members and friends offering support How to recognize if your healthy eating has gone too far Improving your body image and achieving body acceptance How it can help with anxiety, depression, PTSD, substance abuse, and more How to recognize and stop emotional and stress eating','[-0.016952576,0.072438285,-0.012350385,0.03805151,-0.048991125,0.0072823577,0.067364715,0.013991773,0.021613851,0.028146066,0.059435077,0.015587336,-0.049451437,0.0103109265,0.0032054249,0.03703092,-0.040726185,0.0035970625,-0.0807174,0.069312654,0.033696875,0.010896423,-0.0105676465,0.013608793,-0.08284185,0.02303301,0.05403187,-0.082273,0.08243919,0.024175353,0.009636184,0.13374,0.014338023,0.0016940563,0.019894665,0.05815687,-0.025459157,0.009215181,-0.018639196,-0.009072366,-0.0037689947,-0.044186685,-0.019825928,-0.070324905,-0.005434201,-0.08784167,-0.044322167,0.032706212,0.045082197,-0.066457585,-0.07417982,-0.007974785,0.019994972,-0.015548612,0.010546348,-0.06863032,0.026437744,0.037068978,-0.052129444,-0.029788747,0.010182801,0.022180747,0.03840602,-0.042710926,0.13817647,0.01257942,0.015689785,0.019809766,0.0066859024,0.046275817,-0.005244644,-0.026281154,-0.01293531,0.04591412,-0.012263513,-0.01943682,-0.05624883,-0.021936594,0.0133369975,0.024122717,0.014516424,0.08981886,0.04320258,-0.004692219,-0.0699302,-0.017793605,-0.04109296,0.019103818,-0.034931835,0.0014568587,-0.01571986,0.020762661,-0.0523879,-0.047275208,-0.031011252,0.0043104743,-0.062251545,-0.01092693