(30227,'Suicide & Self-Harm',2,302,'If you’re feeling suicidal, you may be afraid you’ll be judged or that no one will understand. If you’re worried about someone else, you may fear that you’ll say the wrong thing. But talking openly can save a life. Don’t wait: reach out. How to deal with suicidal thoughts and feelings How to help someone who is suicidal and save a life Learning to heal and move on with your life Tips for overcoming depression one step at a time How to recognize depression in yourself and others Therapy, medication, and lifestyle changes that can help you feel better Surviving the tragedy and trauma of suicide Symptoms, treatment, and self-help for PTSD','[0.07448767,0.09131174,-0.041174036,0.005340843,-0.10315851,0.0046127443,0.072209366,0.021841792,-0.016744096,-0.0326975,0.10679388,-0.007325821,-0.03427403,-0.014319737,0.04808041,-0.009992016,0.05918064,-0.018111005,-0.04219119,-0.049554735,0.021252505,-0.036450878,-0.056950763,-0.0315181,-0.08048604,0.0018654099,0.017850665,-0.004228779,0.08466218,-0.059291355,0.00928458,0.057116404,0.07853385,-0.028257556,-0.04736934,0.029496536,0.007691595,-0.051520202,0.031093663,0.015774582,-0.0010991818,-0.09801473,-0.06847605,-0.10110148,0.08754467,-0.020482494,-0.038416103,0.037817877,0.040700592,-0.044971354,-0.08517554,0.034888078,-0.014454817,-0.00961842,0.017860396,-0.16059785,0.034440104,0.027229028,-0.0042061345,-0.011682857,-0.019563701,0.033915725,0.010822282,-0.030658096,0.10385547,-0.015910305,-0.11086473,-0.0082133645,0.024729762,0.038578644,-0.0019508038,-0.06511924,-0.025247082,0.023779681,-0.09808411,-0.049151164,-0.011878583,0.034177143,0.025818435,0.0055382815,-0.0065502645,0.019441353,-0.021272957,0.02969033,-0.09562253,-0.03329686,-0.04293199,0.031110043,-0.049630553,0.01910409,0.023645433,0.07304172,-0.05325058,-0.0737013,-0.032693002,0.023480572,-0.10742042,-0.06403536,-0.01952536,-0.012632354,0.008447965,0.0035181388,-0.03316301,-0.08515345,-0.07049074,0.0011728037,0.014389963,-0.097