(30232,'Illness & Disability',2,307,'Health is often taken for granted, until it’s gone. Whether you’re coping with a disability, a serious illness, or the strain of caregiving, these guides and resources can provide you with hope and strategies for coping with challenges. Chair exercises and fitness tips for people with injuries or disabilities How to overcome challenges and build a fulfilling life Dealing with a diagnosis of cancer, heart disease, or other serious illness Symptoms, depression, and help for COVID long haulers How hearing loss or damage can affect your mental well-being Managing anxiety and making the most of your time with a healthcare provider How to manage pain and improve your mood and outlook','[0.035147753,0.07385368,-0.05992017,0.016353132,-0.04158075,0.010939111,0.07569025,-0.00661624,-0.010843099,-0.033509627,0.07234922,-0.0014856,-0.094847225,-0.027282016,0.05062008,-0.01819376,0.02952213,0.02416334,-0.06909793,-0.08704385,-0.018911026,-0.03153751,-0.022272553,-0.026711853,-0.0047295596,0.0072483066,0.020402377,-0.061349384,0.055875693,-0.074624576,0.03354774,0.07139307,0.058301587,-0.04059007,-0.03207727,0.063952625,-0.01971531,-0.03996063,0.011861036,0.040733878,-0.01269814,-0.042084154,-0.076548904,-0.14149348,0.08704052,-0.071141385,-0.09081434,0.010990757,0.011448896,-0.040207915,-0.062271327,-0.024169521,0.0019523206,-0.013159907,0.056468226,-0.165884,0.021668972,-0.012078732,-0.0023037835,-0.040248275,0.040457927,0.074050926,-0.02818537,-0.02525624,0.031450517,-0.0318954,-0.06221579,0.005032858,0.014236856,-0.015090805,0.002282392,-0.03854034,-0.08002296,0.05217326,-0.07707199,-0.0060708546,0.0087959245,0.035855573,0.029738434,0.041204613,0.017692411,0.059124388,0.0041978825,0.017737918,-0.08728625,-0.013413807,-0.068869255,0.023144802,-0.002160657,0.031309858,0.04592621,0.098071575,-0.04474671,-0.026194056,-0.06460159,-0.020262659,-0.039809015,-0.04014433,-0.04039203,0.044298213,-0.011920663,-0.026635988,-0.022500565,-0.02339929,-0