(30233,'Sexual Health',2,308,'Sexual health is closely linked to mental and emotional health. While some sexual issues can be the result of physical illness or injury, many others stem from psychological issues such as depression, stress, anxiety, and bipolar disorder. Similarly, healthy sex can be a deeply emotional experience. It can help to strengthen your most intimate relationship, boost your mood, and ease stress and anxiety. Coping with online abuse and practicing safe sexting Tips to help you increase intimacy and enjoyment as you get older Tips to regain your sense of control, rebuild your self-worth, and heal','[0.0042146747,0.072003484,-0.07696891,0.043039475,-0.07237456,0.031988565,0.046921156,0.04731483,0.0072288723,-0.008502271,0.045925144,0.0063806563,-0.05750054,-0.04768197,0.082203545,0.07148743,0.0147577515,0.030340217,-0.004206877,0.0043745893,0.015721086,-0.042303283,-0.07747003,-0.010564244,-0.0096732015,0.06551295,-0.0065260376,-0.026739452,0.08408527,-0.0041230554,0.049995422,0.04652387,0.044832334,0.026076032,-0.027067028,0.075341545,-0.045179486,0.017538475,0.00576641,0.011950976,-0.058794145,-0.024506288,-0.06147763,-0.11003201,0.034556683,-0.061696272,-0.03258554,-0.025331387,-0.019549757,-0.107876875,-0.035232726,-0.008439274,0.042662602,0.006280594,0.008938437,-0.066776976,0.0420188,0.038028717,-0.025616368,0.08304992,-0.01657538,0.021513157,0.056610603,-0.030296708,0.104336366,0.048373785,-0.07796407,-0.034303594,0.03421647,-0.0021107998,0.0133404145,-0.07029324,-0.032601837,0.04233079,-0.040144324,0.0000020521536,-0.015453564,-0.011257272,0.07195683,0.031455774,-0.004705838,0.082729585,-0.02606856,0.013163342,-0.010584487,-0.02870964,-0.0056225024,0.04225994,-0.10296355,0.08850084,0.02012022,-0.046677403,-0.0066987015,-0.095424674,0.06538994,-0.011440415,-0.057186518,-0.0040213917,-0.0039028754,0.015892353,0.03205854,0.029295944,-0.04597866,0.022131307,-0.1126297,-0.030543666,0.10586063,-0.12577464,-0.009519744,-0.0058902907,-0.1338524