(30236,'Teen Issues',2,310,'The teenage years can be full of pressure, uncertainty, and change. But you’re not alone and you can feel better. These resources can help you (and your parents) tackle common challenges—from depression to bullying and eating disorders. Dealing with anger, violence, delinquency, and other behaviors Improving your body image and achieving body acceptance Coping with online abuse and practicing safe sexting Tips for kicking your cigarette habit for good Tips for breaking free of compulsive smartphone use The health risks in young people and how to quit','[0.005216372,0.10743238,-0.024583198,0.008905906,-0.07423765,-0.013390407,0.08290085,0.015540846,0.0183627,0.015516115,0.105074726,0.00171313,-0.011116941,-0.022421282,0.0841683,0.047442198,0.016846573,-0.002053658,-0.040537532,-0.03584004,-0.0051803864,-0.012415235,-0.061765254,0.0309476,-0.073958255,0.043518588,0.0068313614,-0.04277161,0.035148297,-0.00317625,-0.020538343,0.046931915,0.0063011893,-0.006947894,-0.09797975,0.10842896,0.029890489,0.022987485,0.040630944,-0.0042465003,-0.03721983,-0.025207225,-0.012238113,-0.10612013,0.08179673,-0.07128779,-0.08141449,0.01727614,0.0016633028,-0.10288855,-0.102701694,0.08401529,-0.0014845391,0.0338187,0.052106954,-0.13084748,0.05830673,0.065898016,0.035565976,0.026002401,-0.01827045,0.025027173,0.042841807,-0.057572566,0.12504902,-0.04225644,-0.104174934,-0.00929915,0.011123508,0.0034985219,-0.014957054,-0.05603478,-0.03039393,0.032912362,-0.07952951,-0.018944543,-0.028852956,0.035747852,0.05729858,0.039447535,0.0076261265,0.04807341,0.019701513,-0.004540057,-0.035332747,-0.0018891862,-0.047587544,0.029200228,-0.023106435,0.025898451,0.02301537,0.039665524,-0.06085491,-0.01939568,-0.027168587,-0.052413333,-0.11230401,-0.009847155,-0.035723083,0.052777417,0.030514713,0.015701432,-0.0690369,-0.050088942,-0.06923296,-0.033675104,0.009523344,-0.11510284,-0.03231276,0.028091423,-0.15550384,-0.0875333,-0.082716174,-0.08678297,0.017702041,0.025310153