(30242,'BMKG Prediksi Pasang Laut Tinggi Awal Januari 2026, Ini Wilayah Pesisir Kaltim yang Terdampak',2,316,'Lebih dari 3 miliar penduduk dunia menggantungkan mata pencarian pada kekayaan laut. Akan tetapi, 30 persen ikan dunia ditangkap secara cuma-cuma dan tidak bertanggung jawab. Angka tersebut jauh di bawah level kemampuan untuk memproduksi hasil laut berkelanjutan. Pembangunan berkelanjutan menciptakan kerangka kerja guna melindungi ekosistem laut dan pantai dari polusi yang berasal dari darat serta menyadarkan dampak pengasaman samudera. Campaign yang mendorong inovasi bisnis dan penerapan sustainability development untuk UMKM Lokal','[-0.020102909,0.06935515,0.032399252,0.0478654,-0.10123668,0.0070824707,0.02865458,0.013018325,0.010950029,-0.037370913,0.092932336,-0.041137494,-0.030636737,-0.05305144,0.034869958,-0.009011013,0.016296163,0.00447972,-0.0877864,-0.06469006,0.025032366,-0.0111637395,-0.030867357,-0.016579477,-0.032104466,0.027936857,0.0025053266,-0.0032225887,0.096645154,0.0057232627,0.0013092586,0.1595018,-0.006522023,-0.054422125,-0.062051352,0.06412714,-0.026134206,-0.052443467,0.05275697,0.024243867,-0.014921174,-0.09120119,-0.002262452,-0.13672724,0.06467178,-0.033894222,-0.07621462,0.026272964,-0.002708118,-0.004878366,-0.057036612,0.036637004,0.0059431586,0.0007274109,-0.03532722,-0.145535,0.0052536805,-0.008559667,0.008010052,-0.011768654,0.020337906,0.030410731,-0.016767234,-0.029492998,0.12518744,-0.043314725,-0.08860446,0.026889952,0.04578176,-0.017142884,-0.04262154,-0.020991394,0.026062204,0.087128796,-0.0962365,-0.022272404,0.020840388,-0.0018751568,-0.0050709834,0.019887151,0.058488343,0.02484853,0.053706642,-0.021861741,-0.09462265,0.0005634152,-0.025313642,0.065409414,-0.06188812,0.011348748,0.057110228,0.0637784,-0.058115494,-0.021590684,-0.05135264,-0.0081708105,-0.10110121,-0.0029298614,-0.012091149,0.03235598,-0.012534818,-0.020873856,-0.037788574,-0.0400619,-0.0749268,-0.07050186,-0.015077723,-0.097875424,0.04635162,0.01795